{
  "texts": [
    "Potential Misuse: Any research involving the development or disclosure of potential vulnerabilities carries the risk of being misused by malicious actors.",
    "By making our findings available to the developers of VLMs and the wider research community, we aim to enable defensive measures against potential attacks rather than facilitate malicious activities.",
    "We encourage collaboration and promote the collective effort to address and mitigate potential security risks",
    "In conclusion, while our research exposes a potential vulnerability in VLMs, the findings of this work can promote awareness of VLM safety issues and call for future efforts to address them.",
    "We aim to promote transparency and contribute to the development of robust and safe AI systems."
  ]
}